item.title: CVE-2023-40072|2024-02-28T23:11:06.830Z -- elecom%20co.%2Cltd. -- wab-s600-ps
item.description: OS command injection vulnerability in ELECOM network devices allows an authenticated user to execute an arbitrary OS command by sending a specially crafted request. Affected products and versions are as follows: WAB-S600-PS all versions, WAB-S300 all versions, WAB-M1775-PS v1.1.21 and earlier, WAB-S1775 v1.1.9 and earlier, WAB-S1167 v1.0.7 and earlier, and WAB-M2133 v1.3.22 and earlier.
